JSON schema generator.
Definitions:
IJsonSchemaCollection
OpenAPI v3.0
OpenAPI v3.1
When you need JSON schema, do not write it by yourself, but just call typia.json.schemas() function.If you call the typia.json.schemas() with specialization of target Schemas, typia will analyze your Schemas and generate JSON schema definition in the compilation level. However, note that, JSON schema definitions of "OpenAPI v3.0" and "OpenAPI v3.1" are a little bit different. Therefore, you have to consider which value to assign in the Version argument.
